column5: For those interested.......ENJOY and Good Luck Fishing.  http://www.buffalonews.com/sports/other/fishing-line/article848100.ece
Hey Thanks for posting this. I want to learn the eastern end better this year and having this bookmarked will help alot.  darren

You've seen the perch catches recently courtesy of Billy Bob and Court R, also a 5 fish box of 30lbs for smallies or 40+ lbs for Walleyes is a realistic goal here. Been fishing here since the late 50's and it has never been better than now.
Thanks billy bob...  That was a good read...
